dct_title_s: Port facilities at port of New York, Hudson River, New Jersey; Weehawken and West New York
dct_description_sm: Nautical chart showing the port facilities in the Hudson River at the Port of New York, New Jersey
Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection
Soundings are expressed in feet and tenths below local plane of mean low water as determined from gauge set by U.S. Engineer Office.
Soundings taken approximately 2 ft. from face of pier or bulkhead.
Soundings taken from Mar. 7 to Mar 20, 1934
